            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "Yes, we have tightened up (improved) the self-injections for macros. Feel free to customize the injection queries if you want different highlighting.\r\n\r\n(And homebrew nightly \"releases\" -- as opposed to actual releases -- don't come with treesitter parsers, so make sure this is not the issue you're seeing. Also make sure you're not using the nvim-treesitter queries, which may - intentionally -- differ.)",
